* io.Writer
.code ./misc/interfaces.go /6_1 OMIT/,/END 6_1 OMIT/
- _0<=n<=len(p)_ - n - written bytes
- writer must return error if it returns n < len(p)
- writer mustn't modify p
- don't retain buffer, copy it if needed


